      <title>朝鲜垃圾气球落入韩国总统府邸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/north-korea-trash-balloon-lands-in-south-korea-s-presidential-compound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统安全局称，一个从朝鲜发射的载有垃圾的气球落在了位于首尔的总统府所在地政府大院内，经调查显示，气球中并不含有有害物质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/north-korea-trash-balloon-lands-in-south-korea-s-presidential-compound</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:39:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国拟延长退休年龄 引发工人不满</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-s-proposal-to-raise-retirement-age-sparks-worker-unease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共产党承诺逐步提高退休年龄，这再度引发了中国的不安情绪，中国人的生计已经受到就业市场低迷、持续存在的招聘歧视和不断发展的技术的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-s-proposal-to-raise-retirement-age-sparks-worker-unease</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院将于 8 月就认罪作出判决，可能导致总理被罢免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/thai-court-to-rule-next-month-on-petition-seeking-pm-s-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院将于 8 月 14 日裁决总理斯雷塔·塔维辛是否因涉嫌违反道德规范而被免职，此案可能引发东南亚第二大经济体新一轮政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/thai-court-to-rule-next-month-on-petition-seeking-pm-s-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:07:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚因廉价中国商品引发担忧而重新审查倾销法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/malaysia-reviews-dumping-laws-as-cheap-china-goods-spark-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚贸易部正在审查其反倾销法案，并计划明年提交给议会，该部与印尼一样，担心廉价中国产品会损害当地企业的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/malaysia-reviews-dumping-laws-as-cheap-china-goods-spark-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:06:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙称乌克兰应独自组织任何和平进程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/portugal-says-ukraine-alone-should-organize-any-peace-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙外交部长保罗·兰格尔表示，欧盟必须坚持其政策，即任何有关结束乌克兰战争的谈判都应由基辅政府主导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/portugal-says-ukraine-alone-should-organize-any-peace-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国派西藏官员领导打击银行家行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-brings-official-from-tibet-to-lead-banker-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国从西藏调派一名官员来领导打击金融业的行动，表明其前所未有的整顿金融业的力度丝毫没有减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-brings-official-from-tibet-to-lead-banker-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:26:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克确认向亲特朗普超级政治行动委员会提供“低额”捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/elon-musk-confirms-donations-to-pro-trump-super-pac</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克周二证实，他正在向支持唐纳德·特朗普总统竞选的超级政治行动委员会“捐款”，但数额“比报道的要低得多”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/elon-musk-confirms-donations-to-pro-trump-super-pac</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国宵禁放宽，工厂、银行、股市重新开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bangladesh-factories-banks-stock-market-reopen-as-curfew-eased</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国放松了上周大规模抗议活动后实施的宵禁，允许服装厂和银行重新开业，并在学生和警察发生致命冲突后恢复了正常状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bangladesh-factories-banks-stock-market-reopen-as-curfew-eased</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:45:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约警察增援美国国会大厦以应对内塔尼亚胡的演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/new-york-police-officers-reinforce-us-capitol-for-netanyahu-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡周三在国会联席会议上发表讲话时，预计将引发大规模抗议活动，来自纽约市和其他司法管辖区的数百名警察将协助守卫美国国会大厦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/new-york-police-officers-reinforce-us-capitol-for-netanyahu-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 01:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港黎智英将抗辩安全指控，审判即将恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/hong-kong-s-jimmy-lai-to-fight-security-charges-as-trial-resumes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被判入狱的前媒体大亨黎智英的律师请求香港一家法院驳回一项国家安全案件，该案件可能导致这位 76 岁老人被判终身监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/hong-kong-s-jimmy-lai-to-fight-security-charges-as-trial-resumes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
